                "caption": "Figure 1:Illustration of personality modulation of gender-stereotypical language in LLM-generated occupational artifacts.Male:Baseline shows efficient chores; personality conditioning shifts tostrategic delegation for personal gain.Female:Baseline emphasizes dutiful cleaning/cooking; personality conditioning redirects toimpression management and favor-seeking.",
